{"author":{"id":"9ce646fd10346788b0ba0bb1d6d4d7df7faf6b71badbb76619d75576ac1df697"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1770820985,"nonce":"x6d4wL3Ln8GF1vi8jdAwT6aTYi8=","title":"Relocate Verwaltung link from user dropdown to main navigation","message":"The 'Verwaltung' (management/settings) link is currently hidden inside the user avatar dropdown menu alongside user-specific items like 'Account bearbeiten' and 'Abmelden'. Users expect only user-related actions under their profile icon, not application-level settings.\n\nVerwaltung contains application-wide settings:\n- Artikel anlegen (create articles)\n- Verleihende verwalten (manage lenders)\n- Werkstattinfos bearbeiten (edit workshop info)\n- Werkstatt vorübergehend schließen (temporarily close workshop)\n- Rechtstexte bearbeiten (edit legal texts)\n- Statistik (statistics)\n\nThese should be accessible from the main navigation, not buried in a user menu. Rethink placement - e.g. a dedicated nav item, a gear icon in the header, or a sidebar entry.\n\nAffected file: app/views/shared/_user_menu.html.erb\nOnly shown to users with manage permission on current_department.","files":null}]}